  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      In the present study, the effects of 3 weeks of unloading on muscle mass and muscle fiber
      characteristics will be determined. In addition, the effects of 6 weeks of recovery will be
      assessed.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
