  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Healthy

          -  BMI &lt; 30 kg/m2

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Use of medication that may affect haemostasis

          -  Subjects with (recent) musculoskeletal/orthopaedic disorders known to affect the
             outcome of the study or that compromise their ability to walk with crutches

          -  Subjects with metal implants in their lower limbs

          -  Subjects with known cardiovascular and/or haemostasis disorders

          -  Subjects with known severe hypertension
      </textblock>
